\c 4
\s IJerusalema izakuba lodumo
\p
\v 1 Labesifazana abayisikhombisa bazabamba indoda ibenye ngalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x*\x + Jobe 5.19.\x*\x + 3.6.\x*\x + 3.25. Hlab. 78.63.\x*, bathi: Sizakudla okwethu ukudla, sigqoke ezethu izigqoko; kuphela ibizo lakho kalibizwe phezu kwethu; susa ihlazo lethu\x + Gen. 30.23.\x*.
\v 2 Ngalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x* ihlumela leN\nd kosi\x + 11.1. Jer. 23.5. 33.15. Zek. 3.8. 6.12. Luka 24.27.\x*\nd* lizakuba ngelobuhle, njalo elodumo, lesithelo selizwe ngesokuhle kakhulu lokokubukeka\x + 13.19. 28.1,3, 5.\x* kwabaphunyukileyo bakoIsrayeli.
\v 3 Kuzakuthi-ke oseleyo eZiyoni lotshiywe eJerusalema athiwe ungcwele\x + Obad. 1.17.\x*, wonke obhalelwe\x + Luka 10.20. Heb. 12.23. Eks. 32.32.\x* impilo eJerusalema;
\v 4 iNkosi isigezisile ingcekeza\x + Mal. 3.2,3.\x* yamadodakazi eZiyoni\x + 3.16.\x*, yahlambulula amacala egazi eJerusalema\x + Hez. 40.38.\x* phakathi kwayo, ngomoya wesahlulelo langomoya wokutshisa.
\v 5 LeN\nd kosi\nd* izadala phezu kwayo yonke indawo yokuhlala yentaba yeZiyoni, laphezu kwenhlangano zayo ezibiziweyo, iyezi emini, lentuthu\x + Eks. 13.21.\x*, lokukhanya\x + Zek. 2.5.\x* komlilo olamalangabi ebusuku\x + Eks. 13.21.\x*; ngoba phezu kwayo yonke inkazimulo kuzakuba lesembeso esiluphahla.
\v 6 Njalo kuzakuba ledumba\x + Isam. 7.15.\x* libe ngumthunzi emini ekutshiseni\x + 25.4. 16.3. 32.2.\x*, njalo libe yisiphephelo\x + 25.4. Hlab. 27.5.\x*, njalo libe yisivikelo esivunguvungwini lezulwini\x + 16.4.\x*.
